item.title: You Won't Believe the Trick to Winning Tim Hortons Roll Up the Rim!
item.description: You Won’t Believe the Trick to Winning Tim Hortons Roll Up the Rim! Roll Up the Rim is back at Tim Hortons, and it’s time to get your game face on! This beloved Canadian tradition has been around for over 30 years and is a great way to win prizes like free coffee, donuts, and even cars. But how do you make sure you’re the one taking home the prizes? Here are three tips to help you win at Roll Up the Rim:
